<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50 to-white px-8 py-6 border-b border-gray-100">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <i class="fas fa-house text-4xl text-orange-600"></i>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Gospel at Home</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="p-8 pb-12">
      <!-- Description Section -->
      <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Gospel at Home is a Spiritist practice aimed at promoting spiritual harmony and strengthening family bonds through reflection on the teachings of Jesus Christ as found in the Gospel According to Spiritism.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-400 rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
            "At least once a week, gather your family and compliment them with the joy of Spiritism, implementing the Gospel practice so that Jesus' teachings can be an effective route of love and wisdom in your home…"
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6">
          Strengthen your spiritual connection and bring peace to your home. By dedicating time to study and reflection, we create a peaceful atmosphere where Jesus' teachings can guide our daily lives toward higher purpose and harmony.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Guide Section -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-compass mr-2 text-orange-500"></i>
          Quick Guide
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 font-bold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">1</span>
                <span>Choose a consistent day and time for your gathering. All are welcome - family, friends, or even individual practice.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 font-bold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">2</span>
                <span>Prepare water to be blessed during the meeting.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 font-bold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">3</span>
                <span>Begin with a spontaneous prayer to open hearts to reflection.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 font-bold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">4</span>
                <span>Read and reflect on a passage from The Gospel According to Spiritism.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 font-bold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">5</span>
                <span>Share practical applications of the teachings in daily life.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 font-bold rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0">6</span>
                <span>Conclude with a prayer of gratitude, keeping the entire gathering to about 30 minutes.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Note:</strong> The Gospel at Home is not a mediumistic meeting but a simple gathering focused on moral and spiritual enlightenment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service Details Cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <!-- Left Card -->
        <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-orange-800 flex items-center mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-clock mr-2"></i>
            Session Details
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
              <span>Maximum of 30 minutes spiritual session</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
              <span>Conducted in your home</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
              <span>No special preparation needed</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Card -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 flex items-center mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-water mr-2 text-orange-500"></i>
            Preparation
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
              <span>Provide glasses of water for each participant</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
              <span>Choose a quiet space</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-orange-500 mr-2 mt-1"></i>
              <span>Open heart and mind</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Book Downloads Section -->
      <div class="mt-8 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center">
          <i class="fas fa-file-pdf mr-2 text-orange-500"></i>
          Study Materials
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- English Version -->
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="bg-orange-100 w-full md:w-40 h-48 flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-lg p-4">
                <i class="fas fa-file-pdf text-5xl text-orange-600 mb-3"></i>
                <span class="text-xs text-orange-800 text-center">English Version</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">The Gospel According to Spiritism</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Allan Kardec</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The complete moral teachings of Jesus with Spiritist interpretation.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <%= link_to asset_path("The-Gospel-According-to-Spiritism-Allan-Kardec.pdf"),
                      download: "The Gospel According to Spiritism - Allan Kardec.pdf",
                      class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors" do %>
                  <i class="fas fa-download mr-2"></i> Download PDF
                <% end %>
                <%= link_to asset_path("The-Gospel-According-to-Spiritism-Allan-Kardec.pdf"),
                      target: "_blank",
                      class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors" do %>
                  <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt mr-2"></i> View Online
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Portuguese Version -->
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="bg-orange-100 w-full md:w-40 h-48 flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-lg p-4">
                <i class="fas fa-file-pdf text-5xl text-orange-600 mb-3"></i>
                <span class="text-xs text-orange-800 text-center">Versão em Português</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">O Evangelho Segundo o Espiritismo</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Allan Kardec</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Os ensinamentos morais de Jesus com interpretação espírita.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <%= link_to asset_path("O-Evangelho-Segundo-o-Espiritismo-Allan-Kardec.pdf"),
                      download: "O Evangelho Segundo o Espiritismo - Allan Kardec.pdf",
                      class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors" do %>
                  <i class="fas fa-download mr-2"></i> Download PDF
                <% end %>
                <%= link_to asset_path("O-Evangelho-Segundo-o-Espiritismo-Allan-Kardec.pdf"),
                      target: "_blank",
                      class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors" do %>
                  <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt mr-2"></i> View Online
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Guide Downloads -->
          <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-4">Practical Guides</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <!-- English Guide -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="bg-orange-100 p-3 rounded-lg mr-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-book-open text-orange-600 text-xl"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Gospel at Home Guide</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Step-by-step instructions for your spiritual practice</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                      <%= link_to asset_path("Gospel-At-Home-Guide.pdf"),
                            download: "Gospel-At-Home-Guide.pdf",
                            class: "inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white rounded-lg text-xs font-medium transition-colors" do %>
                        <i class="fas fa-download mr-1"></i> Download
                      <% end %>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Portuguese Guide -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <div class="bg-orange-100 p-3 rounded-lg mr-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-book-open text-orange-600 text-xl"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Guia do Evangelho no Lar</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Instruções passo-a-passo para sua prática espiritual</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                      <%= link_to asset_path("Evangelho-No-Lar-Guide.pdf"),
                            download: "Evangelho-No-Lar-Guide.pdf",
                            class: "inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white rounded-lg text-xs font-medium transition-colors" do %>
                        <i class="fas fa-download mr-1"></i> Download
                      <% end %>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Back Button -->
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 rounded-lg text-gray-700 font-medium transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i>
          Back to Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
